turn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531223\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qei1665702543515.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qei1665702543515.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qei1665702543515.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qei1665702543515\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation that is called before a request for a web service is actually sent. If the operation cannot be found, processing continues.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qei1665702543515__topic_d37376e1_d37377e1_d37378e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE\nparams\n string <var class=\"keyword varname\">Envelope</var> : INOUT\n string <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var> : IN\n string <var class=\"keyword varname\">OperationName</var> : IN\nendparams\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Your Code here ...</var>\nend;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qei1665702543515__section_rjb_yyr_pcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1105497e69\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qei1665702543515__ul_vdz_yyr_pcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qei1665702543515__li_d19052e1_d19053e1_d19054e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Envelope</var>—content of the SOAP\n          envelope. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qei1665702543515__li_d19055e1_d19056e1_d19057e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>—name of the web\n          service component. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qei1665702543515__li_d19058e1_d19059e1_d19060e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">OperationName</var>—name of the\n          operation on <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var> that is being activated. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qei1665702543515__section_m5h_zyr_pcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1105497e96\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__2\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__1\">0 <p class=\"p\">&gt;1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__2\">Operation succeeded and processing can continue.\n              </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__1\">1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__2\">Fast track response. No web service is actually\n                called, no further callbacks, pre or post, are called and the returned envelope is\n                treated as the response. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__1\">&lt;0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qei1665702543515__table_d3761e1_d3762e1_d3763e1__entry__2\">Operation failed to successfully process the SOAP\n                envelope. Further processing of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> statement in the\n                SOAP connector will be aborted. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qei1665702543515__section_gyb_wzr_pcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1105497e160\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qei1665702543515__p_d37388e1_d37389e1_d37390e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE</span> operation is\n        invoked by the SOAP connector before it actually sends the SOAP message containing the\n        activation request to the web service. The operation can be used to add SOAP header elements\n        or encrypt the data in the SOAP envelope.</p>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"qei1665702543515__p_d37391e1_d37392e1_d37393e1\">\n<div class=\"div snippetText\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qei1665702543515__p_d37394e1_d37395e1_d37396e1\">The names of the parameters are optional. Any other\n            change to the interface, such as additional parameters or a different operation name,\n            cause the operation to fail.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"qei1665702543515__note_hwg_xzr_pcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The SOAP connector does not verify the correctness of\n        the envelope returned by a callback operation. It is used as-is, so the callback operation\n        is responsible for ensuring that it is well-formed and correct.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531223\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531223\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE Operation that is called before a request for a web service is actually sent. If the operation cannot be found, processing continues. operation SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE params string Envelope : INOUT string ComponentName : IN string OperationName : IN endparams Your Code here ... end; Copy Parameters Envelope —content of the SOAP envelope. ComponentName —name of the web service component. OperationName —name of the operation on ComponentName that is being activated. Return Values Value Meaning 0 >1 Operation succeeded and processing can continue. 1 Fast track response. No web service is actually called, no further callbacks, pre or post, are called and the returned envelope is treated as the response. <0 Operation failed to successfully process the SOAP envelope. Further processing of the activate statement in the SOAP connector will be aborted. Description The SOAP_CALLOUT_PRE operation is invoked by the SOAP connector before it actually sends the SOAP message containing the activation request to the web service. The operation can be used to add SOAP header elements or encrypt the data in the SOAP envelope. The names of the parameters are optional. Any other change to the interface, such as additional parameters or a different operation name, cause the operation to fail. Note: The SOAP connector does not verify the correctness of the envelope returned by a callback operation. It is used as-is, so the callback operation is responsible for ensuring that it is well-formed and correct. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}